WEBVTT

00:01.102 --> 00:03.704
*

00:15.683 --> 00:18.186
A diversion?

00:18.219 --> 00:19.820
Why?

00:21.055 --> 00:22.423
So we can get in.

00:22.456 --> 00:23.891
Yeah, I got that part.

00:23.924 --> 00:26.360
Why?

00:26.394 --> 00:29.563
Remember when we used
to get high, and you'd ask,

00:29.597 --> 00:31.399
every time, "Why is it blue?"

00:31.432 --> 00:33.033
And I would say,
"It's always blue, man."

00:33.067 --> 00:34.168
Y-Yeah, except
that never happened.

00:34.202 --> 00:35.669
That's a fake memory.

00:35.703 --> 00:37.505
I-I didn't meet you
till the hospital.

00:37.538 --> 00:39.039
But you remember it, right?

00:39.073 --> 00:40.941
Fake, real, you remember it!

00:40.974 --> 00:43.177
So it happened.

00:43.211 --> 00:45.213
Are you you at all?

00:45.246 --> 00:48.449
Lenny from the-the hospital,
the corn flake girl?

00:48.482 --> 00:50.851
Who couldn't stand
the word "nipples"?

00:50.884 --> 00:53.621
Or is this just a... a mask?

00:53.654 --> 00:55.856
Does it matter?

00:55.889 --> 00:58.259
Bodies and minds, humanity.

00:58.292 --> 01:01.095
Nobody has ever asked a puma
its opinion.

01:01.129 --> 01:04.198
Or a stalk of asparagus
how it feels.

01:04.232 --> 01:07.701
My associate is who she needs
to be at this moment.

01:10.738 --> 01:13.274
Look, all I know
is she said to help you--

01:13.307 --> 01:15.909
Syd-- and I love her,
I trust her,

01:15.943 --> 01:19.313
so... I-I will.

01:19.347 --> 01:21.749
Just, no more lies.
If we're gonna do this,

01:21.782 --> 01:24.618
if I'm gonna help you
find your body,

01:24.652 --> 01:26.620
you're gonna give me back
my friends,

01:26.654 --> 01:29.223
and we're gonna do whatever
she-- Syd, future Syd--

01:29.257 --> 01:32.260
whatever she says.

01:32.293 --> 01:36.797
But let me be ultra clear:
nobody gets hurt.

01:40.033 --> 01:42.035
You got it?

02:00.954 --> 02:02.756
OLIVER:
He agreed.

02:02.790 --> 02:05.193
We go tonight.

02:24.812 --> 02:26.180
OLIVER 2:
Don't worry.

02:26.214 --> 02:27.881
We'll find it.

02:35.589 --> 02:37.591
*

