That was my first guess,
as well.

07:34.154 --> 07:36.289
No. I-I can't shake the feeling

07:36.323 --> 07:39.527
that somehow I constructed it,
this-this orb.

07:40.961 --> 07:44.264
Believe me,
I know how that sounds, yes.

